      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/arts/music/ruth-slenczynska-dead.html</guid>
      <atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/arts/music/ruth-slenczynska-dead.html" rel="standout"></atom:link>
      <description>Treated brutally, she went from celebrated child star to 15-year-old “burned-out candle.” Against the odds, she later resumed performing.</description>
